<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>Rudrohom Mail</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body>
    <div style="max-width: 900px; margin: 15px auto; border: 1px solid #fff; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;">
        <div style="padding: 20px 15px; text-align: center;border:1px solid #666">
            <img src="http://rudrohom.com:1337/images/email/logo.png" alt="" style="width:200px;height:100%;object-fit: contain;">
        </div>
        <div
            style="background-image: url('http://rudrohom.com:1337/images/email/main.jpg');height: 322px;background-position: center;background-size: cover;">
            <h3
                style="font-size: 34px;color:#fc8230;text-align:center;padding: 136px 0px;margin: 0;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);">
                Thanks! Your Booking has been Confirmed for staying at {{hotel_name}}</h3>
        </div>
        <div style="background: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px 15px; color: #333; font-size: 14px;">
            <div>
                <p style="font-size: 16px;line-height: 24px;">
                    Dear {{name}},
                </p>
            </div>

            <p style="font-size: 16px;line-height: 24px;">
                Thank you for choosing <strong>{{hotel_name}}</strong>. We look forward to hosting your stay. <br><br>
                Here are your booking details: <br>
                Booking Confirmation Number: <strong>{{booking_id}}</strong><br>
                Arrival date: <strong>{{arrival_date}}</strong><br>
                Departure date: <strong>{{departure_date}}</strong><br>
                Address: {{hotel_address}}, {{hotel_city}}, {{hotel_state}}<br><br>
                If you require any type of assistance, please call {{hotel_mobile}} || {{hotel_landline}} or email at
                {{hotel_email}}. <br><br>
                We look forward to welcoming you in {{hotel_city}} soon!<br><br>
                <strong>{{hotel_name}}</strong>
            </p>
            <p style="padding: 10px;text-align:center;">
                <a href="#" target="_blank"
                    style="border-radius: .3rem;color:#FFFFFF;background-color:#fc8230;border-radius:0px;display:inline-block;text-decoration:none;text-align:center;padding:10px 30px;">
                    <span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 16.8px;">Jusbid.com</span>
                </a>
            </p>
            <p style="font-size: 16px;line-height: 24px;">Thank you,</p>
            <p style="font-size: 16px;line-height: 24px;">Team Rudrohom.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>